  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promote the Satisfaction of Victims&apos; Rights to Truth, Justice, Reparation and Non-Repetition Through the Strengthening of the Office of the Attorney General of the Nation (PGN) for the Participation of Victims to the Comprehensive System of Truth, Ju</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The intervention seeks to increase the effective participation of victims in the Comprehensive System for Truth, Justice, Reparation and Non-repetition (SIVJRNR) through the strengthening of the Attorney General&apos;s Office (PGN) so that their rights to truth, justice, reparation and non-repetition can be satisfied. In order to achieve these purposes, this project provides for interrelated components that foster the satisfaction and protection of the rights of victims in the face of the peacebuilding process as favorable conditions for a stable and lasting peace.</narrative>
  </description>
